==== How to test ====
- copy the mu.img on the SD card
- edit config.txt
- start the screen command:

$> screen /dev/ttyUSB0 115200
Hello world!
0x00000020


- detach: "Ctrl-a + d"
- exit: "Ctrl-a \"
- reattach: 
  $> screen -r
- list sessions:

$ screen -ls
There is a screen on:
        25789.pts-1.nuc (10/21/17 13:50:47)     (Detached)
1 Socket in /var/run/screen/S-petrum.

- reattach to specific session: 
  $> screen -r 25789.pts-1.nuc

